\section{Installation}

\subsubsection*{R package}
The RedeR package is freely available from Bioconductor at \url{http://bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/html/RedeR.html}.

\subsubsection*{Java application}
The RedeR jar file is already included in the R package and, as usual, to run Java applications your system should have a copy of the JRE (Java Runtime Environment, version>=5).

